posts.description: I stand for the community, always. It was an honor to help re-open the @crenshawymca this week with family, friends, community leaders & young kids who will take part in a very special #WhyNot Academy program this summer. Blessed to use my platform to empower & change lives for generations to come. Big thanks to @jumpman23 @whynotfoundation @mrflowerfantastic!

Happy Father’s Day LovvveOnee! You have always showed me the way and I’m grateful to have you in my life every step of the way. Thank you for each and every life lesson, my role model always. Enjoy your day OG!! Love you Dad!

Dream beyond expectations #whynot. Last night we celebrated the world premiere of the short film WHY NOT? which is inspired by a mentality that I have honored in every aspect of my life. Very proud of the cast & crew for telling a story about finding your purpose and owning it. This is just the beginning!

My ManMan, HAPPY 4th Birthday to my son! You’re such a blessing beyond anything I could imagine. Your energy, your smile, and your amazing spirit is what bring me joy each and everyday. I love you more than life itself and grateful to be your dada. HAPPY BIRTHDAY NOAH🎉🥳🎉🥳🎉🎂🎂

Let’s normalize uplifting and empowering women every single day. Simply because that is what they do for us. Women are the cornerstone of our society, and I’m grateful to share my new EMPOWERMENT color way. Inspired by the colors of the WNBA, I created this shoe in celebration of women all over the world.

#whynot
